content: I'm trying to get a better sense of the financial situation with my grandparents' old farm. Can you help me understand what kind of expenses I should expect if we decide to rent the property out, aside from property taxes? By the way, I've been going through some storage units I rented to store some of the farm's contents, and it got me thinking - the cost of renting a storage unit is not specified in the text, but it can be inferred that it is not zero.
